summary: Just on the northern coast of Lake Ilinalta, a humble fishing shanty was built with the intention of selling live bait and tackle, but for reasons unknown the place is left abandoned.
descriptionHtml:
Just on the northern coast of Lake Ilinalta, a humble fishing shanty was built with the intention of selling live bait and tackle, but for reasons unknown the place is left abandoned.

Perfect for your fish-harvesting needs as salmon and various lake fish are kept within tanks here. There is also a cooking pot available to cook the fish in. Just don't cut yourself on the Dirty Filet Knives available here.

This shack does reset, so don't store your gear in it! Purely for aesthetics.

Check out my other mods on my workshop page in Steam!
author: rtherein
